room_title: Escape room "Steampunk Adventure" by To Escape in Lawrence
room_description: Adam Steampunk made a time machine and has traveled to the future. He left his research behind and needs to get it back. You have been sent to Adam Steampunk's apartment. Your mission is to find his research and activate his travel machine to send it to him. Time is of the essence as he is getting ready to move on.
